{
  "stem": "18281.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And if there is one place in this world that could be considered the birth place of the Holocaust, it certainly was the city of Vienna, where a down and out Adolf Hitler, he lived in very bad conditions in, in some men's homes where the unemployed lived.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He tried to sell his paintings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They threw him out of the academy of, of, of the painters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They-- he tried to, to learn how to paint.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then they said he had no talent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they threw him out of there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But he then saw how the mayor of the city of Vienna got elected every time on an anti-Semitic ticket and that being an outspoken anti-Semite would be a political asset for him.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He also read the writings and rantings of famous anti-Semites in Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "One of them was called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he published a pamphlet, a anti-Semitic pamphlet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "That's where Hitler learned his craft.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And eventually, then he moved on to Germany and became a soldier in the German Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they eventually locked him up in prison at Lansberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And while he was in prison, he wrote his famous",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Vienna has escaped to a great extent the bombardments of other major cities of Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only major damage downtown was the, the great cathedral, which can only be compared to the one in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while that tremendous church built in the 11th century was not damaged by bombs, but it was burned by the, by the SS.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the SS falsely heard reports that the dome in Cologne had been bombed, they burnt the St.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stephen's Cathedral in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The was-- OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vienna a city of about two million people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had about 200,000 Jews in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
